'''Mkhulu Malusi Manqoba Skenjana''' (yavutse 6 Mata 1982), uzwi '''Khulu Skenjana,''' ni umukinnyi wa  [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]]  . <ref name="briefly">https://briefly.co.za/68163-jafta-mamabolo-bio-age-wife-tv-shows-movies-nominations-profile.html</ref> Azwi cyane ku ruhare rwe muri televiziyo izwi cyane ya ''Machine Gun Preacher'', ''Zulu'' na ''Zama Zama'' .

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 6 Mata 1982 i Soweto, muri Afurika y'Epfo. 

Yashakanye na mugenzi we bakina filime Mona Monyane . Bashakanye muri 2016 bamarana imyaka ine hamwe nabana babiri. <ref>https://www.sowetanlive.co.za/entertainment/2020-03-10-mona-monyane-khulu-skenjana-part-ways-after-four-years-of-marriage/</ref> Umwana we wa kabiri Amani-Amaza Wamazulu Skenjana yavutse ku ya 16 Ugushyingo 2017 apfa nyuma y'iminsi irindwi avutse. <ref>https://www.news24.com/drum/celebs/actress-mona-monyane-reflects-on-losing-her-second-child-we-still-miss-our-little-maza-20190624</ref> Umukobwa we w'imfura ni Ase-Ahadi Lesemole Mamphai Skenjana wavutse muri Kanama 2016. <ref>https://www.news24.com/drum/celebs/mona-monyane-and-khulu-skenjana-separate-the-battles-we-have-met-have-been-difficult-to-overcome-together-20200306</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Kuva mu myaka ya za 2000 yatangiye gukina abashyitsi batagaragara muri serivise za tereviziyo nka ''Ahantu hitwa Urugo'', ''Binnelanders'' na ''Generations'' . Hagati aho, yagaragaye muri televiziyo izwi cyane ya ''All Access Mzansi'' maze ahindura nk'umuhanzi w'ijwi. Hanyuma yagaragaye muri serial ''Entabeni'' akina 'Kumkani Modise'. <ref name="tvsa">https://www.tvsa.co.za/actors/viewactor.aspx?actorid=8201</ref>

Muri 2008, yakinnye nka 'Mandla' muri mini-serie ya ''Nowa'' kuva muri Nyakanga kugeza Kanama. Muri uwo mwaka, yagize uruhare rukomeye muri NBC ya ''The Philanthropist'' . Maze mu 2010, we yagize uruhare 'Dawidi Tabane' mu ''biganiro yimije Game.'' Hagati aho, yagaragaye afite uruhare rwa 'Thomas' mu rukurikirane rwa ''Hola Mpinji'' . Yagaragaye kandi muri ''serivise nyinshi zizwi nka'' ''Sokhulu & Partners'', ''Rhythm City'', ''Hola Mpinji'', ''A Place Called Home'' and ''Jozi-H'' . <ref name="tvsa" />

Mu mwaka wa 2011, yatangiye gukina filime afite uruhare 'Max' muri filime ''48'' . Muri uwo mwaka, yagaragaye muri filime ''Machine Gun Preacher'' . Muri 2013, yakinnye cyane 'Themba' muri film ''Zulu'' . Muri uwo mwaka, yinjiye muri saison ya kabiri ya ''Intersexions'' hanyuma muri ''Tempy Pushas'' . 

